Washington Post on ABC
on Wednesday reveals
a majority, 56 percent

05:57.333 --> 06:01.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
of Americans say Trump
is interfering with the
Russia investigations,
rather than cooperating.

06:02.533 --> 06:04.200 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
His approval ratings are
relatively low right now.

06:04.200 --> 06:06.233 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Brandon, let me start with you.

06:06.233 --> 06:10.366 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BRANDON SMITH: Well, Indiana
is as much Trump country
as you are going to find.

06:10.366 --> 06:13.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
He won the state here
by 19 points in 2016.

06:13.966 --> 06:18.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I'm sure that number
isn't as strong as it was in
November, but it's still pretty

06:18.633 --> 06:20.666 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
