06:30.433 --> 06:32.133 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Ashton Marra?

06:32.133 --> 06:35.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
ASHTON MARRA: Yes, I
think the same is true
here in West Virginia.

06:35.233 --> 06:39.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
