of the things that are happening
that we have already talked

06:50.166 --> 06:54.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
about, things at the local
level, like this small
bump in the coal industry.

06:54.200 --> 06:57.566 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Jon
Ralston, Nevada being
a purple to blue state?

06:57.566 --> 07:02.566 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JON RALSTON: Yes, Nevada,
as you know, Trump lost
here by a couple of points.

07:03.733 --> 07:05.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
You have essentially
three states here.

07:05.466 --> 07:07.966 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
