little bit Democratic now when
it comes to presidential races.

07:38.366 --> 07:40.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
So it's three states.

07:40.433 --> 07:43.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I don't think anyone's
views are changing because
of what's happened so far.

07:43.800 --> 07:47.633 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: All right,
well, all three of your states
have Senate contests in the

07:47.633 --> 07:50.533 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
